             was indicted for <rs id="t18220703-62-off329" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220703-62-off329" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220703-62-off329" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220703-62-cd330" type="crimeDate">2d of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220703-62-off329 t18220703-62-cd330"></join>, one handkerchief, value 2 s., two sovereigns, one crown, value 5 s., and two half-crowns, value 5 s., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220703-62-victim594" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Perkins
                        <interp inst="t18220703-62-victim594" type="surname" value="Perkins"></interp>
